<section id="quality" class="gp-quality">
  <div class="gp-wrap">
    <div class="gp-section-head">
      <div>
        <div class="gp-section-num">III &middot; Quality</div>
        <h2 class="gp-section-title" data-ko-block>측정되지 않는 답은<br/><em>맺히지</em> 않습니다</h2>
        <h2 class="gp-section-title" data-en-block>An answer<br/>that <em>can't be measured</em><br/>doesn't ripen</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="gp-section-sub" data-ko-block>Gopedia의 모든 변경은 IR(Information Retrieval) 지표로 검증됩니다. 세계수가 흔들릴 때마다 — 우리는 그 흔들림을 측정합니다.</p>
      <p class="gp-section-sub" data-en-block>Every change to Gopedia is verified by Information Retrieval metrics. Whenever the World Tree shifts — we measure how it shifts.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="gp-ir-grid">
      <div class="gp-ir-chart" id="ir-chart">
        <div class="gp-ir-chart-title">
          <span data-ko-block>RAG 품질 &middot; v1.4 &rarr; v1.7</span>
          <span data-en-block>RAG quality &middot; v1.4 &rarr; v1.7</span>
          <span class="gp-ir-scale">0 &mdash; 1.0</span>
        </div>
        <div class="gp-ir-bars">
          <div class="gp-ir-bar"><div class="gp-ir-name">Recall@10<small>v1.4 baseline</small></div><div class="gp-ir-track"><div class="gp-ir-fill alt" data-w="68"></div></div><div class="gp-ir-v alt">.68</div></div>
          <div class="gp-ir-bar"><div class="gp-ir-name">Recall@10<small>v1.7 current</small></div><div class="gp-ir-track"><div class="gp-ir-fill" data-w="89"></div></div><div class="gp-ir-v">.89</div></div>
          <div class="gp-ir-bar"><div class="gp-ir-name">nDCG@10<small>v1.4 baseline</small></div><div class="gp-ir-track"><div class="gp-ir-fill alt" data-w="54"></div></div><div class="gp-ir-v alt">.54</div></div>
          <div class="gp-ir-bar"><div class="gp-ir-name">nDCG@10<small>v1.7 current</small></div><div class="gp-ir-track"><div class="gp-ir-fill" data-w="81"></div></div><div class="gp-ir-v">.81</div></div>
          <div class="gp-ir-bar"><div class="gp-ir-name">Faithfulness<small>v1.4 baseline</small></div><div class="gp-ir-track"><div class="gp-ir-fill alt" data-w="71"></div></div><div class="gp-ir-v alt">.71</div></div>
          <div class="gp-ir-bar"><div class="gp-ir-name">Faithfulness<small>v1.7 current</small></div><div class="gp-ir-track"><div class="gp-ir-fill" data-w="94"></div></div><div class="gp-ir-v">.94</div></div>
          <div class="gp-ir-bar"><div class="gp-ir-name"><span data-ko-block>인용 정확도</span><span data-en-block>Citation acc.</span><small>v1.4 baseline</small></div><div class="gp-ir-track"><div class="gp-ir-fill alt" data-w="62"></div></div><div class="gp-ir-v alt">.62</div></div>
          <div class="gp-ir-bar"><div class="gp-ir-name"><span data-ko-block>인용 정확도</span><span data-en-block>Citation acc.</span><small>v1.7 current</small></div><div class="gp-ir-track"><div class="gp-ir-fill" data-w="92"></div></div><div class="gp-ir-v">.92</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="gp-ir-legend">
          <span><i style="background:var(--bark-2)"></i><span data-ko-block>이전 (v1.4)</span><span data-en-block>previous (v1.4)</span></span>
          <span><i style="background:var(--moss)"></i><span data-ko-block>현재 (v1.7)</span><span data-en-block>current (v1.7)</span></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="gp-ir-copy">
        <h3 data-ko-block>매주 <em>1,200건</em> 의 질문으로<br/>나무를 흔들어 봅니다.</h3>
        <h3 data-en-block>We shake the tree<br/>with <em>1,200 queries</em><br/>every week.</h3>
        <p data-ko-block>Gopedia는 자체 평가 데이터셋(<strong>Gold Set</strong>)을 통해 매 릴리스마다 Recall, nDCG, Faithfulness, Citation Accuracy를 측정합니다. 숫자가 떨어지는 변경은 절대 머지되지 않습니다.</p>
        <p data-en-block>Gopedia maintains its own <strong>Gold Set</strong> evaluation suite — every release is scored on Recall, nDCG, Faithfulness, and Citation Accuracy. A change that drops the numbers never lands.</p>
        <div class="gp-ir-foot" data-ko-block>* 내부 한국어 + 영어 1,200쿼리 기준 &middot; 2024-12 측정</div>
        <div class="gp-ir-foot" data-en-block>* internal Korean + English 1,200-query set &middot; measured 2024-12</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .gp-quality{background:var(--paper-2);border-top:1px solid var(--rule);border-bottom:1px solid var(--rule);padding:100px 0}
  .gp-ir-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:56px;align-items:center}
  @media(max-width:880px){.gp-ir-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
  .gp-ir-chart{background:var(--paper);border:1px solid var(--rule);padding:32px;position:relative}
  .gp-ir-chart-title{font-family:var(--display);font-style:italic;font-size:16px;color:var(--moss);margin-bottom:20px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:baseline}
  .gp-ir-scale{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10.5px;color:var(--ink-2);font-style:normal;letter-spacing:.1em}
  .gp-ir-bars{display:grid;gap:20px}
  .gp-ir-bar{display:grid;grid-template-columns:130px 1fr 56px;gap:14px;align-items:center}
  .gp-ir-name{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:12.5px;color:var(--ink-2)}
  .gp-ir-name small{display:block;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.12em;color:var(--bark);text-transform:uppercase}
  .gp-ir-track{height:22px;background:repeating-linear-gradient(90deg,transparent 0,transparent 19px,var(--rule-2) 19px,var(--rule-2) 20px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--rule);position:relative}
  .gp-ir-fill{position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:1px;background:var(--moss);width:0;transition:width 1.4s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1)}
  .gp-ir-fill.alt{background:var(--bark-2)}
  .gp-ir-v{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12.5px;color:var(--moss);text-align:right}
  .gp-ir-v.alt{color:var(--bark-2)}
  .gp-ir-legend{display:flex;gap:18px;margin-top:18px;font-family:var(--sans);font-size:11px;color:var(--ink-2)}
  .gp-ir-legend i{width:10px;height:10px;display:inline-block;margin-right:6px;vertical-align:middle}
  .gp-ir-copy h3{font-family:var(--display);font-size:36px;font-weight:500;line-height:1.1;margin:0 0 16px}
  .gp-ir-copy h3 em{font-style:italic;color:var(--moss)}
  .gp-ir-copy p{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--ink-2)}
  .gp-ir-foot{margin-top:18px;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--bark);letter-spacing:.04em}
</style>

<script>
  const fills = document.querySelectorAll('.gp-ir-fill');
  const io = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
    entries.forEach((e) => {
      if (e.isIntersecting) {
        const el = e.target as HTMLElement;
        el.style.width = el.dataset.w + '%';
        io.unobserve(el);
      }
    });
  }, { threshold: 0.3 });
  fills.forEach((f) => io.observe(f));
</script>
